qas.question: How many UEFA Champions League wins does Barcelona have?
What is the  number of UEFA Cup Winners' Cup competitions Barcelona has won?
How many UEFA Super Cup awards does Barcelona have?
What is the number of FIFA Club World  Cup trophies Barcelona has?
What competition is the predecessor to the UEFA Cup-Europa League?

context: As of December 2015[update], Barcelona has won 23 La Liga, 27 Copa del Rey, 11 Supercopa de España, three Copa Eva Duarte[note 2] and two Copa de la Liga trophies, as well as being the record holder for the latter four competitions. They have also won <a0_0>five<a0_0/> UEFA Champions League, a record <a1_0>four<a1_0/> UEFA Cup Winners' Cup, a shared record <a2_0>five<a2_0/> UEFA Super Cup and a record <a3_0>three<a3_0/> FIFA Club World Cup trophies. They also won a record three <a4_0>Inter-Cities Fairs Cup<a4_0/> trophies, considered the predecessor to the UEFA Cup-Europa League.
